OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater firm must get a grip 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon payouts - chancellor    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Chancellor Jeremy Hunt has called for  
OL,6, Thames Water to "get a grip" on        
OL,7, awarding compensation to Surrey        
OL,8, residents who faced problems with their
OL,9, supply for several days.               
OL,11,FThe MP for South West Surrey said      
OL,12,Fhundreds of constituents had complained
OL,13,Fabout the claims system.               
OL,15,FHe also raised concerns that issues    
OL,16,Fover the firm's infrastructure had "not
OL,17,Fbeen resolved" after the loss of water 
OL,18,Fin November.                           
OL,20,FThames Water has since apologised.     
